18.42	Water_tank	Water tank	A water tank is a container for storing water. The need for a water tank is as old as civilized man, providing storage of water for drinking water, irrigation agriculture, fire suppression, agricultural farming, both for plants and livestock, chemical manufacturing, food preparation as well as many other applications.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d6/WaterTank_kwt.JPG/220px-WaterTank_kwt.JPG
